quran[30]{c,v,t}:
  75,1,"aqsm allah subhanah biawm alhisab waljza', waqsm bialnafs almuamanat altqyt alty tlwm sahibuha ealaa tarak altaeat wfiel almwbqat, 'ana alnaas ybethwn. ayznn hdha al'iinsan alkafir 'an lan naqdir ealaa jame eizamah baed tfrqha? bla snjmeha, qadirin ealaa 'an najeal asabeh 'aw anamlh -bed jmeha wtalyfha- khalqana swyana, kama kanat qabl almwt"
  75,2,"aqsm allah subhanah biawm alhisab waljza', waqsm bialnafs almuamanat altqyt alty tlwm sahibuha ealaa tarak altaeat wfiel almwbqat, 'ana alnaas ybethwn. ayznn hdha al'iinsan alkafir 'an lan naqdir ealaa jame eizamah baed tfrqha? bla snjmeha, qadirin ealaa 'an najeal asabeh 'aw anamlh -bed jmeha wtalyfha- khalqana swyana, kama kanat qabl almwt"
  75,3,"'uqsim allah subhanah biawm alhisab waljza', waqsm bialnafs almuamanat altqyt alty tlwm sahibuha ealaa tarak altaeat wfiel almwbqat, 'ana alnaas ybethwn. ayznn hdha al'iinsan alkafir 'an lan naqdir ealaa jame eizamah baed tfrqha? bla snjmeha, qadirin ealaa 'an najeal asabeh 'aw anamlh -bed jmeha wtalyfha- khalqana swyana, kama kanat qabl almwt"
  75,4,"aqsm allah subhanah biawm alhisab waljza', waqsm bialnafs almuamanat altqyt alty tlwm sahibuha ealaa tarak altaeat wfiel almwbqat, 'ana alnaas ybethwn. ayznn hdha al'iinsan alkafir 'an lan naqdir ealaa jame eizamah baed tfrqha? bla snjmeha, qadirin ealaa 'an najeal asabeh 'aw anamlh -bed jmeha wtalyfha- khalqana swyana, kama kanat qabl almwt"
  75,5,"bl yunkir al'iinsan albeth, yurid 'an yabqaa ealaa alfjwr fima yastaqbil min 'ayam emrh, yas'al hdha alkafir mstbedana qiam alsaet: mataa yakun yawm alqyam?"
  75,6,"bl yunkir al'iinsan albeth, yurid 'an yabqaa ealaa alfjwr fima yastaqbil min 'ayam emrh, yas'al hdha alkafir mstbedana qiam alsaet: mataa yakun yawm alqyam?"
  75,7,"f'idha thyar albasar wduhsh fzeana mimaa ra'aa min ahwal yawm alqyamt, wadhahab nur alqmr, wjumie bayn alshams walqamar fi dhahab aldw', fala daw' lawahid mnhma, yaqul al'iinsan wqtha: 'ayn almhrb min aledhab?"
  75,8,"f'idha thyar albasar wduhsh fzeana mimaa ra'aa min ahwal yawm alqyamt, wadhahab nur alqmr, wjumie bayn alshams walqamar fi dhahab aldw', fala daw' lawahid mnhma, yaqul al'iinsan wqtha: 'ayn almhrb min aledhab?"
  75,9,"f'idha thyar albasar wduhsh fzeana mimaa ra'aa min ahwal yawm alqyamt, wadhahab nur alqmr, wjumie bayn alshams walqamar fi dhahab aldw', fala daw' lawahid mnhma, yaqul al'iinsan wqtha: 'ayn almhrb min aledhab?"
  75,10,"fa'iidha thyar albasar wduhsh fzeana mimaa ra'aa min ahwal yawm alqyamt, wadhahab nur alqmr, wjumie bayn alshams walqamar fi dhahab aldw', fala daw' lawahid mnhma, yaqul al'iinsan wqtha: 'ayn almhrb min aledhab?"
  75,11,"lys al'amr kama ttmnah- 'ayuha al'insan- min talab alfrar, laa malja lak wala mnja. 'iilaa allah wahdah masir alkhlayq yawm alqiamat wmstqrhm, fyjazy kla bima ysthq"
  75,12,"lys al'amr kama ttmnah- 'ayuha al'insan- min talab alfrar, laa malja lak wala mnja. 'iilaa allah wahdah masir alkhlayq yawm alqiamat wmstqrhm, fyjazy kla bima ysthq"
  75,13,"yukhabbar al'iinsan fi dhalik alyawm bjmye aemalh: min khayr wshr, ma qddamh minha fi hayatah wama akhkharh"
  75,14,"bl al'iinsan hujat wadihatan ealaa nafsih tlzmh bima faeal 'aw trk, walaw ja' bikuli maedhiratan yaetadhir biha ean 'ijramh, fa'iinah la yanfaeuh dhlk"
  75,15,"bl al'iinsan hujat wadihatan ealaa nafsih tlzmh bima faeal 'aw trk, walaw ja' bikuli maedhiratan yaetadhir biha ean 'ijramh, fa'iinah la yanfaeuh dhlk"
  75,16,"la taharuk -ayha alnby- bialquran lisanak hin nuzul alwhy; li'ajal 'ana ttejl bhfzh, mkhaft 'ana ytfllat mnk. 'iina ealayna jameh fi sdrk, thuma an tqrah bilisanik mataa shyt. fa'iidha qrah ealayk rasulina jbryl fastmie lqra'th wanst lh, thuma aqrah kama aqrak 'iyah, thuma 'iina ealayna tawdih ma ashkl ealayk fhmh min meanyh wahkamh"
  75,17,"la taharuk -ayha alnby- bialquran lisanak hin nuzul alwhy; li'ajal 'ana ttejl bhfzh, mkhaft 'ana ytfllat mnk. 'iina ealayna jameh fi sdrk, thuma an tqrah bilisanik mataa shyt. fa'iidha qrah ealayk rasulina jbryl fastmie lqra'th wanst lh, thuma aqrah kama aqrak 'iyah, thuma 'iina ealayna tawdih ma ashkl ealayk fhmh min meanyh wahkamh"
  75,18,"la tuharik -ayha alnby- bialquran lisanak hin nuzul alwhy; li'ajal 'ana ttejl bhfzh, mkhaft 'ana ytfllat mnk. 'iina ealayna jameh fi sdrk, thuma an tqrah bilisanik mataa shyt. fa'iidha qrah ealayk rasulina jbryl fastmie lqra'th wanst lh, thuma aqrah kama aqrak 'iyah, thuma 'iina ealayna tawdih ma ashkl ealayk fhmh min meanyh wahkamh"
  75,19,"la taharuk -ayha alnby- bialquran lisanak hin nuzul alwhy; li'ajal 'ana ttejl bhfzh, mkhaft 'ana ytfllat mnk. 'iina ealayna jameh fi sdrk, thuma an tqrah bilisanik mataa shyt. fa'iidha qrah ealayk rasulina jbryl fastmie lqra'th wanst lh, thuma aqrah kama aqrak 'iyah, thuma 'iina ealayna tawdih ma ashkl ealayk fhmh min meanyh wahkamh"
  75,20,"lys al'amr kama zemtm- ya maeshar almshrkyn- 'an la baeath wala jza', bal 'antum qawm tuhibuwn aldunya wzyntha, wttrkwn alakhirat wneymha"
  75,21,"lys al'amr kama zemtm- ya maeshar almshrkyn- 'an la baeath wala jza', bal 'antum qawm tuhibuwn aldunya wzyntha, wttrkwn alakhirat wneymha"
  75,22,"wjwh 'ahl alsaeadat yawm alqiamat mushriqatan hasanatan naemt, taraa khalqha wmalk amrha, fttmte bdhlk"
  75,23,"wjwh 'ahl alsaeadat yawm alqiamat mushriqatan hasanatan naemt, taraa khalqha wmalk amrha, fttmte bdhlk"
  75,24,"wwjwh alashqya' yawm alqiamat eabst kalht, tatawaqae 'an tunazal biha musibat ezymt, tqsm faqar alzzahr"
  75,25,"wwjwh alashqya' yawm alqiamat eabst kalht, tatawaqae 'an tunazal biha musibat ezymt, tqsm faqar alzzahr"
  75,26,"hqqana 'iidha wasalat alruwh 'iilaa aealy alsdr, waqal bed alhadirin lbed: hal min raq yarqyh wyashfyh mimaa hu fyh? wayqn almhtdr ann aladhi nazal bih hu firaq aldnya; lmeaynth malayikat almwt, watslt shdt akhar aldunya bshdt 'awal alakhrt, 'iilaa allah taealaa msaq aleabbad yawm alqyamt: 'iimaa 'iilaa aljanat wa'iimaa 'iilaa alnar"
  75,27,"hqqana 'iidha wasalat alruwh 'iilaa aealy alsdr, waqal bed alhadirin lbed: hal min raq yarqyh wyashfyh mimaa hu fyh? wayqn almhtdr ann aladhi nazal bih hu firaq aldnya; lmeaynth malayikat almwt, watslt shdt akhar aldunya bshdt 'awal alakhrt, 'iilaa allah taealaa msaq aleabbad yawm alqyamt: 'iimaa 'iilaa aljanat wa'iimaa 'iilaa alnar"
